"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係歷史科</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到好尷尬"},{"pid":"354173fb678758afaebf3185a4514d80361b059b","tid":461774,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係歷史科</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到好尷尬</blockquote><br />\n其實最尾個段有講到通識嘅"},{"pid":"c2da063a17c594eeecadb33e4cc1b61a96feaf9f","tid":461774,"uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係歷史科</blockquote><br />\n係喎<br />\n我發雞盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfec2ac2e692989f0174c86e20b5b2e811923b1c","tid":461774,"uid":73454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"所有政客r支持時都係開大量空頭支票，<br />\n相信由古代開始所謂起義已經係咁樣。"},{"pid":"9c566a82360a9b8cdd666eafa49204d538d648a0","tid":461774,"uid":57513,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中共一開頭d口號真係好撚正,但估唔到講一套做一套,中晒伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20世紀最大騙案</blockquote><br />\n我老母講佢早兩代親戚係國民黨算中層,<br />\n有個係空軍做直頭搾住架飛機叫佢其他親戚上機逃亡去台灣。<br />\n有兩個唔肯走,話中共應該唔會咁差,結果比人批鬥慘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde36f1fef987623e135840072a65bcacf55e424","tid":461774,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個好似係歷史科</blockquote><br />\n係喎<br />\n我發雞盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a07865a7adeaa7ac0223090fbc1db37c9b7908","tid":461774,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇得出唔係洗腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如問你點睇得出係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係呢個題目上有人話係定唔係咩?<br />\n一條問題睇落中立就代表全個通識都唔洗腦?<br />\n用下腦先出post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又講唔出邊忽洗腦<br />\n又剩係識話人洗腦<br />\n咁空洞一定係通識拎5*"},{"pid":"f82b4d316c35cd96affabf15db6ab913c864d55f","tid":461774,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇得出唔係洗腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如問你點睇得出係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係選毛澤東既大話黎講<br />\n<br />\n咁已經係誤導<br />\n<br />\n老毛一冇心抗日，二冇心搞民主，<br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰答案咩中共全力抗日都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老毛事實上係諗一分抗日，二分應付，七分發展<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東主張共軍和日軍夾擊國民黨軍，毛說：「一些同志認為日軍占地越少越好，後來才統一了認識，讓日軍多占地方才是愛國。否則變蔣介石的國了。國中有國，蔣、日、我，三國志。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg&h=09f19153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb55a4f10cf13107d920d4d852be44eaac875dad","tid":461774,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有政客r支持時都係開大量空頭支票，<br />\n相信由古代開始所謂起義已經係咁樣。</blockquote><br />\n所以在野黨變執政黨之前，無論佢地講咩都要先打個折，唔好信足，因為太多先例。<br />\n雖然香港人冇機會煩哩方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaa4c8a7f1a9cab1f11ce30af6169bc06f93af0","tid":461774,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/113634_e9f59b3a10ced29fd8acde6faa7773a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F113634_e9f59b3a10ced29fd8acde6faa7773a6.jpg&h=80dd04ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好撚尷尬,啲廢老藍絲睇到會有咩感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e1d1f68478e179cf715d0aa47d6ea8f89276a1","tid":461774,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"當初唔止中國d知識份子 甚至美國佬都俾毛魔呃左  以為毛魔支持民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698c703f63e1260e033df19239abb8f8ee5f1365","tid":461774,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾個賈雨村盲撚柒咗就深潛啦<br />\n仲喺度磨爛蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80652a7a2f5fdb11b324fa6acd8799a2be385dc4","tid":461774,"uid":73454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"當時好多人都好熱血咁去建設新中國，<br />\n我覺得好大程度受當時行緊共產主義既蘇聯影響，<br />\n認為中國真係會成為另一個同英美睇齊既大國。"},{"pid":"507b4b65796ba0b3e17fdf956cf953efd63eb076","tid":461774,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇得出唔係洗腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如問你點睇得出係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係選毛澤東既大話黎講<br />\n<br />\n咁已經係誤導<br />\n<br />\n老毛一冇心抗日，二冇心搞民主，<br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰答案咩中共全力抗日都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老毛事實上係諗一分抗日，二分應付，七分發展<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東主張共軍和日軍夾擊國民黨軍，毛說：「一些同志認為日軍占地越少越好，後來才統一了認識，讓日軍多占地方才是愛國。否則變蔣介石的國了。國中有國，蔣、日、我，三國志。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg&h=09f19153&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n中史教科書都有寫一分抗日，二分應付，七分發展 有年問過"},{"pid":"c620055ca9d5eb5bed07c62251d9aeb361d709e5","tid":461774,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇得出唔係洗腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如問你點睇得出係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係選毛澤東既大話黎講<br />\n<br />\n咁已經係誤導<br />\n<br />\n老毛一冇心抗日，二冇心搞民主，<br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰答案咩中共全力抗日都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老毛事實上係諗一分抗日，二分應付，七分發展<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東主張共軍和日軍夾擊國民黨軍，毛說：「一些同志認為日軍占地越少越好，後來才統一了認識，讓日軍多占地方才是愛國。否則變蔣介石的國了。國中有國，蔣、日、我，三國志。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F113000_e42b33cae47027a6668a5decc8f943d5.jpg&h=09f19153&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n1時為1945年<br />\n2嗰科係歷史科"},{"pid":"c64bce52726d6255b947ff0c86b0d78964d275be","tid":461774,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老尾個賈雨村盲撚柒咗就深潛啦<br />\n仲喺度磨爛蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下新聞下半部"},{"pid":"81708e1ef4ff4736abd166816d3fb2848dca2d2e","tid":461774,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話通識係洗腦科班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇得出唔係洗腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如問你點睇得出係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係呢個題目上有人話係定唔係咩?<br />\n一條問題睇落中立就代表全個通識都唔洗腦?<br />\n用下腦先出post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又講唔出邊忽洗腦<br />\n又剩係識話人洗腦<br />\n咁空洞一定係通識拎5*</blockquote><br />\n盲左重唔收皮?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我問你由一條中史科問題點可以得出通識科無洗腦呢個結論? 呢個結論係你講既點解要我比證據?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301c0a017e84f24d4e6fd6aa2fb629a34b15ccf0","tid":461774,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f31689d6bdcc67d8472123c29fe906569caf9610","tid":461774,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共當時都講到自己套理念好美好，而家未又係變質</blockquote><br />\n五毛想學人洗底啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9c3c27aabb2f9963c6510f8dec192e30b66884","tid":461774,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老尾個賈雨村盲撚柒咗就深潛啦<br />\n仲喺度磨爛蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下新聞下半部</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過通識係鬥鳩up多過洗腦科多<br />\n答呢啲問題根本要有好充足嘅source,冇就即係流於鳩up<br />\n<br />\n中學老師就成日講答題技巧答題技巧<br />\n咁其實同讀中史/歷史有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係考嘅題材唔同 (講近代中國就更加會overlap添)"},{"pid":"cdd5f8f52301ad13c9f2cf3baaff64294ed8a9f4","tid":461774,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中共當時都講到自己套理念好美好，而家未又係變質</blockquote><br />\n五毛想學人洗底啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一分洗底，兩分應付，七分發展"},{"pid":"c8e14fc308ba36eb329273871581616fafa93a44","tid":461774,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當初唔止中國d知識份子 甚至美國佬都俾毛魔呃左  以為毛魔支持民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當時佢9up時都未真正享受過權力既快感嘛"},{"pid":"75d84d7505c5af76166c6b94bafb1cbb42ee7782","tid":461774,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初唔止中國d知識份子 甚至美國佬都俾毛魔呃左  以為毛魔支持民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當時佢9up時都未真正享受過權力既快感嘛</blockquote><br />\n之後話唔可以有宗教信仰,但自己做左神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ad9bd0f4f87a3522bb7a2779979dd3517a4df7","tid":461774,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82718f008b75e0ba9c9264c960d1ea480ea040d7","tid":461774,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8de97a2c77951cf8348346446dbb5d5c97b5a984","tid":461774,"uid":27830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"毛魔戀棧權位前的確係好過國民政府管治<br />\n可惜為咗權鬥利慾熏心 忘記初衷"},{"pid":"8529cafbfdf757fda3125d0890cdadcb3da1fb76","tid":461774,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/113634_e9f59b3a10ced29fd8acde6faa7773a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F113634_e9f59b3a10ced29fd8acde6faa7773a6.jpg&h=80dd04ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好撚尷尬,啲廢老藍絲睇到會有咩感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"